<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="farther-adj-adv">farther <strong><em>adj &amp; adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fɑːðə(r)/    美 /'fɑːrðər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(空间距离) 更远的 / 地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We watched their ship moving gradually <strong>farther away</strong>.
我们望着他们的船渐渐远去。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The other girls rushed ahead of me and I fell <strong>farther and farther</strong> behind.
其他女孩冲在了我前面，我越落越远。</p></div>

<h3 id="further-farther">辨析 further, farther</h3>
<p>两者都为far的比较级，但是farther只用于本义“(空间距离上的) 更远”。  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Africa is further / farther from England than France.
非洲距离英国比距离法国远。</p></div></div>